{"tid":1177891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那又自慰 美支女主播辯論 支媒分析三點後喊：劉欣是贏家","createTime":"2019-05-30T04:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T09:58:10.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":258,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee5034578c79abbb641b59dd81198c3b7da34c6","tid":1177891,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"中美女主播貿易辯論今早展開，這場辯論賽由中國環球電視網主播劉欣對美國福斯商業頻道女主播雷根（Trish Regan）。具中共官媒背景的微信公眾號「牛彈琴」指出，這場辯論中透露出三個細節，讓大家一眼就知道真正的贏家是劉欣。<br />\n<br />\n第一點，從道理上來說，雷根就輸了，因為中美的事大家都清楚本質是什麼，真相是什麼，雷根自己也強調了，貿易戰對誰都沒有好處，大家應該要拚雙贏，這不恰好是中國的主張嗎？<br />\n<br />\n第二點，從情緒上來看，雷根那種張口就來的台風，真要公平辯論起來，漏洞實在太多。而事實上，劉欣不到30秒的開場白就被雷根至少插話3次。<br />\n<br />\n此外，「牛彈琴」指出，從語言上來比較，一位中國女主播用對方的母語來辯論，這本身就是中國人較開放和智慧的表現；雙方你來我往交流了一番，雷根總體來說保持了風度，但劉欣更沒讓人失望，因為劉欣解釋了諸多外國人都誤解的問題，包含知識產權保護、關稅稅率、國有企業等。<br />\n<br />\n文章分析，一些西方媒體的選擇性甚至歧視性報導貿易戰的內容，加劇了「西強東弱」的不平衡，「正確的批評，我們當然要虛心接受；但莫須有的指責，卻真的有損國家形象和利益，也是我們中國人無法接受的。」<br />\n<br />\n44歲的劉欣現為央視旗下中國環球電視網「欣視點」節目主持人，曾先後任職央視英語國際頻道主持人、央視駐日內瓦記者等。除中文和英語外，還精通法語及土耳其語。<br />\n<br />\n而46歲的雷根是福斯財經網主持人及撰稿人，目前是「雷根黃金時段」節目主持人，曾任職哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）、美國財經新聞網站CNBC及彭博社。"},{"pid":"613c02845769e163a4603bd9c2836b44f27be3d2","tid":1177891,"uid":130695,"like":480,"dislike":0,"score":480,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"不得不服 點解支那人生到咁多賤種<br />\n日日成地精 行過都大肚啦"},{"pid":"ece1ce3006ae1dc7504434fedb88c7eb8c518186","tid":1177891,"uid":170135,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"對住44歲老女人，點樣打飛機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbcc5a95fa48896bb54d02c70888724d53e5b43","tid":1177891,"uid":60333,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"打飛機打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8567c834d4ceb34291228a3a47952e610aa56844","tid":1177891,"uid":32511,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DyHNz0ODGbE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDyHNz0ODGbE&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuiciNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=3d0677cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DyHNz0ODGbE</a>"},{"pid":"39ccb2694d0d49e9e8ebdafec1fd2889006886c8","tid":1177891,"uid":50386,"like":376,"dislike":5,"score":371,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"一位中國女主播用對方的母語來辯論，這本身就是中國人較開放和智慧的表現<br />\n<br />\n兩個唔同國家嘅人要辯論唔用英文唔通用法文"},{"pid":"88d6f333cf9d36edae821cdd9dc6bfeb1d367d05","tid":1177891,"uid":125193,"like":195,"dislike":0,"score":195,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:59:33.000Z","msg":"所以根本冇必要辯論 根本雞同鴨講 指鹿為馬 <br />\n<br />\n好似 Trump 2011年話 同中國冇必要嘈 直接用拳頭打埋佢就OK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ec8e22a03344440b94d18e3e04384ae21e470e","tid":1177891,"uid":56147,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"無睇  燒山話係訪問唔係辯論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受訪者都贏？"},{"pid":"a2ff4bac3bf2038fd00c1e3ff83132d534a60618","tid":1177891,"uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"劉欣被Trish Regan按在地上磨擦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d91886230814cb1c5f40e497900e3d7219d6f0b","tid":1177891,"uid":18569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"就咁文字討論，畫面又冇<br />\n咁都有得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331b7241222078d2771c3174702ef8d2a08527be","tid":1177891,"uid":170135,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"39ccb2694d0d49e9e8ebdafec1fd2889006886c8","tid":1177891,"uid":50386,"like":376,"dislike":5,"score":371,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"一位中國女主播用對方的母語來辯論，這本身就是中國人較開放和智慧的表現<br />\n<br />\n兩個唔同國家嘅人要辯論唔用英文唔通用法文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"梗係用英文la~<br />\n支那人識閪英文咩 , 翻譯完出黎改鳩晒D內容<br />\n支那人咪可以打飛機囉"},{"pid":"bb667076f2237118fb3f02214a8bc69ad5b056db","tid":1177891,"uid":10703,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"quote":{"pid":"39ccb2694d0d49e9e8ebdafec1fd2889006886c8","tid":1177891,"uid":50386,"like":376,"dislike":5,"score":371,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"一位中國女主播用對方的母語來辯論，這本身就是中國人較開放和智慧的表現<br />\n<br />\n兩個唔同國家嘅人要辯論唔用英文唔通用法文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"點解國際語言係英文，唔係匪語<br />\n已經睇到兩個國家軟實力既相差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa613a7af9b8fdcc98ab9b4fc56dfa3d1eea7232","tid":1177891,"uid":32511,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"美中貿易戰一路燒到輿論戰場，美國福斯財經新聞網（Fox Business Network）女主播黎根（Trish Regan）與中國官媒央視旗下的中國環球電視網（CGTN）主播劉欣於今日台灣上午8點30分展開兩國貿易戰大辯論，針對黎根質問中國竊取智慧財產（IP），劉欣竟說「我不否認」存在IP竊盜問題，但自清她不是中國共產黨員、所言代表自己觀點。<br />\n這場號稱「辯論」短短不到15分鐘，其實比較像是黎根主持的福斯財經新聞網節目「黎根黃金時段（Trish Regan Primetime）」就貿易戰相關問題訪問劉欣。<br />\n<br />\n黎根質問：貿易戰對每個人都不好，有許多證據顯示中國偷了數百億美元以上IP，請問劉欣看法？<br />\n<br />\n劉欣回答時表示，許多美國企業都在中國經營，且繼續在中國市場營運，美國總統川普實施的關稅使這些美企經營更困難。但劉欣接著說，「我不否認」中國存在IP竊盜的情形，這也是必須處理的議題，因為沒有處理智慧財產權議題，沒有國家可以成功，這一點共識在中國已建立起來。<br />\n不過，當黎根質問：中國政府2017年立法通過國家安全法令，中國企業和公民必須配合國家情報蒐集，例如華為（Huawei）公司就必須分享許多價值高昂的資訊給官方的問題時，直接造成其他企業和國家的威脅？<br />\n劉欣避重就輕，未回答有關中國國安法令對企業的影響問題，僅稱如果透過雙方「互惠學習」目的，你願意花錢去買我們IP，那就沒有任何問題，「大家可以一起發財」。<br />\n<br />\n這時，黎根馬上回馬槍說，如同劉欣所言，IP必須付費「合法取得」，遵守法律才能相互信任。"},{"pid":"b9dd38cba5a27680096273e695f2736d14021f91","tid":1177891,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"最重要係美國人點睇"},{"pid":"a5080b2075c8958d641b9156a6758d92d7b7a34d","tid":1177891,"uid":47311,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"74ec8e22a03344440b94d18e3e04384ae21e470e","tid":1177891,"uid":56147,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"無睇  燒山話係訪問唔係辯論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受訪者都贏？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"終蟈每秒都贏緊<br />\n幾時冇贏過？"},{"pid":"afb96dd64cfa58f6c34c2662447e3f98974af772","tid":1177891,"uid":33668,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"支那民最鐘意呢D大陸佬打鬼佬嘅戲份 都係反應民族自卑嘅行為"},{"pid":"0b3866e9e66545d2e3c0ca1e58f54e95da3f2645","tid":1177891,"uid":170135,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"afb96dd64cfa58f6c34c2662447e3f98974af772","tid":1177891,"uid":33668,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"支那民最鐘意呢D大陸佬打鬼佬嘅戲份 都係反應民族自卑嘅行為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"我諗起葉問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bf28050ecb902b91ecc96e6b3c32d5cc365fd4","tid":1177891,"uid":32511,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"b9dd38cba5a27680096273e695f2736d14021f91","tid":1177891,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"最重要係美國人點睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"支那主持認左有偷技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cc25c320d65f9658bcae0ae1599ab63db45020","tid":1177891,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"第一同第三點，即使未辯已經贏咗"},{"pid":"7ead27978a3d7e269eea47803f90f725496a6f57","tid":1177891,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47bf28050ecb902b91ecc96e6b3c32d5cc365fd4","tid":1177891,"uid":32511,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"b9dd38cba5a27680096273e695f2736d14021f91","tid":1177891,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"最重要係美國人點睇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"支那主持認左有偷技術<img src=\"/assets